# QuizGenerator Skill

## Purpose
Creates engaging, pedagogically sound quizzes for robotics and AI concepts. Generates multiple-choice questions with clear correct answers, distractors aligned to common misconceptions, and detailed explanations for learning reinforcement.

## Inputs

```yaml
topic:
  type: string
  description: "Robotics/AI concept to quiz on (e.g., 'ROS 2 publisher-subscriber', 'URDF robot modeling', 'Gazebo physics', 'VLA prompt engineering')"
  required: true

difficulty:
  type: string
  enum: [easy, medium, hard]
  description: "Question difficulty level"
  required: true

num_questions:
  type: integer
  minimum: 1
  maximum: 10
  description: "Number of questions to generate"
  default: 5
  required: false

question_types:
  type: array<string>
  enum: [multiple-choice, true-false, fill-in, scenario-based]
  description: "Types of questions to include"
  default: [multiple-choice]
  required: false

learning_outcomes:
  type: array<string>
  description: "Learning outcomes the quiz should assess"
  required: false

context:
  type: object
  description: "Additional context (chapter, module, learner level)"
  properties:
    chapter_title: string
    module_number: integer
    learner_level: string (enum: beginner, intermediate, advanced)
  required: false
```

