```

## Integration

Part of @Educator workflow. Generated after chapter content finalized. Quiz embedded in MDX via `<Quiz>` component:

```mdx
<Quiz questions={generatedQuestions} />
```

Supports tracking learner performance (via backend) for adaptive learning recommendations.

